Note:¶

scheduled_elapsed = scheduled_arrival - scheduled_departure,
actual_elapsed = actual_arrival - actual_departure,
delay_time = actual_arrival(HHMM) - scheduled_arrival(HHMM)
when canceled or diverted == 1, no information for delay
taxi_off, taxi_in, wheels_off, wheels_in, are not accurate and have some problems, and we will not use these information

Get delay table for different airline¶

In [24]:
def get_flight_problem(flights_delay, flights):
    '''
    return the delay type infor dic, with key as airlines id, value is the list for the number of each delay type
    '''
    problem_type = ['cancelled', 'diverted','airline_delay', 'weather_delay','air_system_delay', 'security_delay', 'aircraft_delay',]
    airlines = set(flights_delay["airline_name"])
    airlines_infor = {key:[] for key in airlines}
    for df_tmp in flights_delay.groupby("airline_name"):
        num_problems = [ df_tmp[1][(df_tmp[1][p] != 0.0) & (df_tmp[1][p].notnull())].shape[0] for p in problem_type]
        airlines_infor[df_tmp[0]] = num_problems
        airlines_infor[df_tmp[0]].append(df_tmp[1].shape[0])
        num_only_delay = df_tmp[1][df_tmp[1]["airline_delay"].notnull()].shape[0]
        airlines_infor[df_tmp[0]].append(num_only_delay)
        airlines_infor[df_tmp[0]].append(sum(df_tmp[1][df_tmp[1]["airline_delay"].notnull()]["total_delay_time"]))
        airlines_infor[df_tmp[0]].append(flights[flights["airline_name"]==df_tmp[0]].shape[0])
    return airlines_infor

Airline vs Delay Type¶

Air Carrier: The cause of the cancellation or delay was due to circumstances within the airline’s control (e.g. maintenance or crew problems, aircraft cleaning, baggage loading, fueling, etc.).
Extreme Weather: Significant meteorological conditions (actual or forecasted) that, in the judgment of the carrier, delays or prevents the operation of a flight such as tornado, blizzard or hurricane.
National Aviation System (NAS): Delays and cancellations attributable to the national aviation system that refer to a broad set of conditions, such as non-extreme weather conditions, airport operations, heavy traffic volume, and air traffic control.
Late-arriving aircraft: A previous flight with same aircraft arrived late, causing the present flight to depart late.
Security: Delays or cancellations caused by evacuation of a terminal or concourse, re-boarding of aircraft because of security breach, inoperative screening equipment and/or long lines in excess of 29 minutes at screening areas.

    ("Jetblue", NewYork_EWR_flights, NewYork_EWR_flights_delay, "tab:blue"),
    ("SkyWest", NewYork_LGA_flights, NewYork_LGA_flights_delay, "tab:orange")
]

delay_cols = airdelay_type["airline_related"]

# Loop over each airline/airport dataset
for airline, df_all, df_delay, color in plot_data:
    hours = range(1, 24)
    delay_percentages = []
    
    for hr in hours:
        total_flights = df_all[
            (df_all["airline_name"] == airline) &
            (df_all["scheduled_departure"] == hr)
        ].shape[0]
        
        if total_flights == 0:
            delay_percentages.append(0)
            continue
        
        delayed_flights = df_delay[
            (df_delay["airline_name"] == airline) &
            (df_delay["scheduled_departure"] == hr) &
            (df_delay[delay_cols].sum(axis=1) != 0.0) &
            (df_delay[delay_cols[0]].notnull())
        ].shape[0]
        
        delay_percentages.append(delayed_flights / total_flights)
    
    ax.plot(hours, delay_percentages, marker="o", label=airline, color=color)

# Formatting
ax.set_xticks([3, 6, 9, 12, 15, 18, 21, 24])
ax.tick_params(axis="x", labelsize=12)
ax.tick_params(axis="y", labelsize=12)
ax.set_xlim(1, 24)
ax.set_ylim(0, 1)
ax.set_xlabel("Hour", size=14)
ax.set_ylabel("Delay Percentage", size=14)
ax.legend(fontsize=12)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

Find the best and worst combinations at different time¶

In [66]:
def get_min_max_time(dataset, dataset_delay):
    time_min_list = []
    time_max_list = []
    for i in range(1,25):
        time_min = 1 
        time_max = 0
        time_min_a = None
        time_max_a = None
        df_flights = dataset[dataset["scheduled_departure_hour"] == i]
        df_flights_delay = dataset_delay[ (dataset_delay["scheduled_departure_hour"] == i)&
                                            (sum([dataset_delay[v] for v in airdelay_type["airline_related"]])!= 0.0) & 
                                            (dataset_delay[airdelay_type["airline_related"][0]].notnull())]
        for a in set(df_flights["airline_name"]):
            df_a = df_flights[df_flights["airline_name"] == a]
            if df_a.shape[0] >= 15:
                df_a_delay = df_flights_delay[df_flights_delay["airline_name"] == a]
                p = df_a_delay.shape[0]/df_a.shape[0]
                if p < time_min:
                    time_min = p
                    time_min_a = a
                if p > time_max:
                    time_max = p
                    time_max_a = a
        if time_min_a == None:
            time_min = 0
        if time_max_a == None:
            time_max = 0 
        time_min_list.append([time_min, time_min_a])
        time_max_list.append([time_max, time_max_a])
    return time_min_list, time_max_list

min_list = {}
for i in range(24):
    mins = [min_EWR[i][0], min_LGA[i][0], min_JFK[i][0]]
    mins_a = [min_EWR[i][1], min_LGA[i][1], min_JFK[i][1]]
    idx = [idx for  idx, i in enumerate(mins_a) if i != None]
    if len(idx) != 0:
        min_time = min([mins[i] for i in idx])
        min_time_a = [a for idx, a in enumerate(mins_a) if mins[idx] == min_time and a != None]
        airp = []
        if 0 in [idx for idx, a in enumerate(mins_a) if mins[idx] == min_time and a != None]:
            airp.append("EWR")
        if 1 in [idx for idx, a in enumerate(mins_a) if mins[idx] == min_time and a != None]:
            airp.append("LGA")
        if 2 in [idx for idx, a in enumerate(mins_a) if mins[idx] == min_time and a != None]:
            airp.append("JFK")
        infor = ""
        for j in range(len(airp)):
            if j != len(airp):
                infor += min_time_a[j] + ", " + airp[j] + "; "
            else:
                infor += min_time_a[j] + ", " + airp[j]
        min_list[i] = [min_time, infor]
    else:
        continue
